—First You need to log in as root, once logged in as root Enter these Commands:

CREATE DATABASE bey2ollakdb;
CREATE USER ‘bey2ollak’@‘localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON bey2ollakdb.* TO 'bey2ollak'@'localhost';
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

- It’s all good now you can run the java code file “part2.java” with Command Line using javac to compile the java file first then run using the java command 
Or you can open the Solution with Intellij IDEA

— The Code will perform all the scenarios sequentially, all you have to do is press Enter after Every scenario/attempt to Proceed to the next scenario.
